15 SECTION 1.(b) This section becomes effective June 30, 2025. Property in the
16 territory described in Section 1(a) of this act as of January 1, 2025, is subject to municipal taxes
17 for taxes imposed for taxable years beginning on or after July 1, 2025.
18 SECTION 2.(a) The following described property, identified by Granville County
19 Tax Property Identification Number, is removed from the corporate limits of the City of
20 Creedmoor: 180603417847.
21 SECTION 2.(b) This section has no effect upon the validity of any liens of the City
22 of Creedmoor for ad valorem taxes or special assessments outstanding before the effective date
23 of this section. Such liens may be collected or foreclosed upon after the effective date of this
24 section as though the property were still within the corporate limits of the City of Creedmoor.
25 SECTION 2.(c) This section becomes effective June 30, 2025. Property in the
26 territory described in Section 2(a) of this act as of January 1, 2025, is no longer subject to
27 municipal taxes for taxes imposed for taxable years beginning on or after July 1, 2025.
28 SECTION 3. Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective when it becomes
29 law.
